duties.size = 10se 2: Proctoring

loop each follower shard contacts leader
Follower->+Heart\npump: schedule()
Heart\npump->-Broker: send\nheartbeats
end
Broker->Auditor: analyze
Auditor->Partition\nTable: new shard
loop async agent
Proctor->Partition\nTable: get shards
Proctor->+Proctor: calculate\nstate
Proctor->Broker: send clearance to all good shards
Proctor->-Cluster\nState: update()
end
Broker->Follower: clearance

